@startuml
title UML State Transition Diagram - Video Suggestion System

[*] --> UserSuggestionRequest

state "User suggestion request" as UserSuggestionRequest
state "User identification" as UserIdentification
state "Gather suggested videos" as GatherSuggestedVideos
state "Add video details" as AddVideoDetails
state "Send suggestions" as SendSuggestions

UserSuggestionRequest : entry / Receive suggestion request
UserSuggestionRequest --> UserIdentification

UserIdentification : entry / Identify user
UserIdentification --> GatherSuggestedVideos

Gather
@enduml
